See here: http://www.bempp.org/installation.html


`git clone https://github.com/wangyu9/bemppm.git`

cd bemppm
mkdir build
cd build

cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/media/wangyu/sdb1/WorkSpace/Python/Steklov/libs/libbemppm-1e-2/ ..

make -j4

make install


To edit the default bempp to use:
gedit ~/anaconda/lib/python2.7/site-packages/bempp.pth
